  <brief_title>Operative Versus Conservative Treatment of Scaphoid Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Time to Return to Previous Activity Between Operative Treatment and Cast Immobilization of Complete Fracture of the Middle Part of the Scaphoid Without Dislocation</official_title>
